OL,3,CStar horse dies after breaking leg in
OL,4,Crace fall
OL,6,FThe Jersey-Derby-Winning horse,
OL,7,FCueros, has died after a race on
OL,8,FFriday evening at Les Landes
OL,9,Fracecourse.
OL,11,FJockey Victoria Malzard was riding in
OL,12,Fthe Grosnez Handicap when her horse
OL,13,Ffell and broke its leg whilst turning
OL,14,Finto the home straight.
OL,16,FIn an emotional interview with ITV
OL,17,FNews, she said: "It's just an
OL,18,Funfortunate event that happened. It
OL,19,Ffelt like he slipped and the events
OL,20,Fafter that are a bit of a blur,
OL,21,Feverything happened very quickly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
