OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1783959567
OL,3,CStar horse dies after breaking leg in
OL,4,Crace fall
OL,6,FShe continued by saying that "everyone
OL,7,Fwas quick to react and he wasn't in
OL,8,Fpain for too long, which is the most
OL,9,Fimportant thing".
OL,11,FBoth the jockey and her trainer,
OL,12,FAlyson Malzard, said that events such
OL,13,Fas this are rare in Jersey:
OL,15,F"It's a freak accident and it doesn't
OL,16,Fhappen very often.
OL,18,F"In Jersey, it's very rare. I can't
OL,19,Fremember the last time we lost one on
OL,20,Fthe race course."
